msgctxt "QL_RitoMini_Flint_Desc"
msgid ""
"Jogo is in Rito Village on his honeymoon,\n"
"and he wants his new wife's favorite treat:\n"
"baked apples. The snag in the plan so far\n"
"is that he has no fire to bake with.\n"
"\n"
"Bring Jogo some <1.se_co>flint<2.re_co> so he can light a fire."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_RitoMini_Flint_Finish"
msgid ""
"You gave Jogo, who is honeymooning in\n"
"Rito Village, some flint and received a\n"
"tidy sum of rupees in return.\n"
"\n"
"Jogo is planning to feed his wife as many\n"
"baked apples as he can cook. He'll gladly\n"
"take all the <1.se_co>flint<2.re_co> you're willing to deliver."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_RitoMini_Flint_Name"
msgid "The Spark of Romance"
msgstr ""

